after undergoing heart surgery.

01:19:47.770 --> 01:19:52.620 align:middle line:10%
Paxton leaves his two children
and wife of 30 years behind.

01:19:52.620 --> 01:19:53.970 align:middle line:10%
>> I'm a believer.

01:19:53.970 --> 01:19:57.970 align:middle line:10%
>> Kayna Whitworth,
ABC News, Los Angeles.

01:19:57.970 --> 01:20:00.660 align:middle line:84%
>> I just forgot everything
when you did that.

01:20:00.660 --> 01:20:01.460 align:middle line:90%
Who am I?

01:20:01.460 --> 01:20:02.690 align:middle line:90%
>> You're here at Cannes.

01:20:02.690 --> 01:20:04.230 align:middle line:90%
>> What hole are we playing?

01:20:04.230 --> 01:20:06.570 align:middle line:10%
>> Saw "Into the Wild" recently.

01:20:06.570 --> 01:20:08.530 align:middle line:10%
