01:20:10.537 --> 01:20:11.870 align:middle line:10%
I was thinking about it all day.

01:20:11.870 --> 01:20:15.270 align:middle line:10%
>> That could make a good
double bill to "Mean Dreams."

01:20:15.270 --> 01:20:17.500 align:middle line:10%
Both kind of road
pictures, on the road.

01:20:17.500 --> 01:20:18.825 align:middle line:10%
You end up in a bus.

01:20:18.825 --> 01:20:19.700 align:middle line:90%
